  "page": "Lord of Parchments",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Parchments</b> is a title claimed by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\">House Penrose</a> of the castle <a href=\"/index.php/Parchments\" title=\"Parchments\">Parchments</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Parchments\">Known Lords of Parchments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Parchments&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Parchments\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Penrose\" title=\"Ronnel Penrose\">Ronnel Penrose</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_baelor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_baelor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Penrose\" title=\"Lord Penrose\">Lord Penrose</a>, the father of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cortnay_Penrose\" title=\"Cortnay Penrose\">Cortnay Penrose</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Parchments&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_king